 lang=EN-US>12</span>米<span lang=EN-US>*10<span
 lang=EN-US><span lang=EN-US>米</span></span><span lang=EN-US>；217</span></span>演播厅的表演区域为<span
 lang=EN-US>8</span>米<span lang=EN-US>*6</span>米，<span lang=EN-US>202</span>演讲厅的表演区域为<span
